  Stable for HPPA (bug #268138).

  13 Oct 2009; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> postgresql-base-8.4.ebuild:
  Stable for HPPA (bug #285475).

  11 Oct 2009; Patrick Lauer <patrick@gentoo.org>
  postgresql-base-7.4.ebuild, postgresql-base-8.0.ebuild,
  postgresql-base-8.1.ebuild, postgresql-base-8.2.ebuild,
  postgresql-base-8.3.ebuild, postgresql-base-8.4.ebuild:
  Changing virtual order and dropping old pgsql for 8.3 and 8.4 to unconfuse
  package managers. Thanks to grobian for noticing.

  01 Oct 2009; Tobias Klausmann <klausman@gentoo.org>
