  03 May 2009; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> postgresql-base-8.3.ebuild:
  Add ~s390

  19 May 2008; Tiziano Müller <dev-zero@gentoo.org>
  postgresql-base-7.3.ebuild, postgresql-base-7.4.ebuild,
  postgresql-base-8.0.ebuild, postgresql-base-8.3.ebuild:
  Marked 7.3,7.4,8.0 stable on alpha amd64 arm hppa ia64 ppc ppc64 s390 sh
  sparc x86 since they have dev-db/libpq-{7.3,7.4,8.0} stable. Dropped ~s390
  and ~sparc-fbsd keyword for 8.3 ({postgresql,libs}-8.3 are p.masked
  anyway).

